---
title: Mexican Style Fried Chicken Wraps with Cheddar, Chips and Sweet Chilli Sauce
description: These Mexican Style Fried Chicken Wraps are a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
